{"item_id":"d4760927ed:0","text":"PxrCookieLightFilter 会在灯光前方投射绘制纹理。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:1","text":"这个 light filter 是以下节点的更完整版本："}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:2","text":"PxrGoboLightFilter"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:3","text":"Parameters（参数）"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:4","text":"Cookie Mode"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:5","text":"指定 cookie mode："}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:6","text":"Physical (0)"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:7","text":"：cookie 的行为类似一扇彩色玻璃窗，灯光从中穿过。falloff 和 blur 由灯光尺寸、到灯光的距离以及与 cookie 的距离决定。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:8","text":"Analytic (1)"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:9","text":"：cookie 具有固定投影，并提供手动 blur 和 falloff 控制。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:10","text":"Map"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:11","text":"投射纹理的文件名。如果想控制投射边缘的 blur，请将 mask 包含在此贴图的 alpha channel（alpha 通道）中。否则，当 Blur > 0.0 时，它会使用安装在 $RMANTREE/lib/textures/white.tex 的白色不透明 alpha 来进行模糊。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:12","text":"Fill Color"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:13","text":"如果纹理的 tile mode（平铺模式）不重复，此项指定投射矩形外部以及后方区域的颜色。当下面指定 Blur 时，投射矩形边缘会与填充颜色混合。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:14","text":"Width"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:15","text":"灯光穿过的矩形宽度。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:16","text":"Height"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:17","text":"灯光穿过的矩形高度。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:18","text":"Multiplier"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:19","text":"Density"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:20","text":"控制投射效果的强度。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:21","text":"Invert"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:22","text":"指定在应用之前是否反转投射纹理。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:23","text":"Intensity"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:24","text":"下方 diffuse 和 specular 贡献的全局 Multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:25","text":"Diffuse"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:26","text":"此 light filter 结果用于 diffuse contribution 的 multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:27","text":"Specular"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:28","text":"此 light filter 结果用于 specular contribution 的 multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:29","text":"Projection (For Analytic Mode Only)"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:30","text":"Directional"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:31","text":"当开启此项时，纹理会使用正交投影沿某个方向投射。关闭时，纹理会使用由 Apex 指定的焦点进行投射。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:32","text":"Shear X"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:33","text":"沿 X axis 对投影进行剪切。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:34","text":"Shear Y"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:35","text":"沿 Y axis 对投影进行剪切。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:36","text":"Apex"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:37","text":"cookie 中心与投影中心之间的距离。仅当 Directional 关闭时适用。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:38","text":"Use Light Direction"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:39","text":"如果开启此项，投影方向由光源中心的位置决定。否则，它只会跟随 cookie 的方向。WARNING：这不适用于 dome 和 mesh lights。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:40","text":"Texture Mapping"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:41","text":"Tile Mode"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:42","text":"指定纹理如何重复。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:43","text":"No Repeat (0)"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:44","text":"Edge Extent (1)"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:45","text":"Tile (2)"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:46","text":"Invert U"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:47","text":"仅当你想左右翻转纹理时才开启此项。默认情况下，纹理方向会与在图像查看器中看到的方向一致。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:48","text":"Invert V"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:49","text":"仅当你想从下到上翻转纹理时才开启此项。默认情况下，纹理方向会与在图像查看器中看到的方向一致。请注意，light filter 已经考虑了 V 方向翻转，以得到正确的默认方向。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:50","text":"Scale U"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:51","text":"投射纹理在 U direction 上的 scale。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:52","text":"Scale V"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:53","text":"投射纹理在 V direction 上的 scale。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:54","text":"Offset U"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:55","text":"投射纹理在 U direction 上的 offset。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:56","text":"Offset V"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:57","text":"投射纹理在 V direction 上的 offset。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:58","text":"Use Alpha"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:59","text":"如果关闭此项，结果可能不够平滑。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:60","text":"Premultiplied Alpha"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:61","text":"如果使用未预乘 Alpha 的纹理，请将此项设为 0 或关闭，以获得正确行为。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:62","text":"Blur (for Analytic Mode Only)"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:63","text":"Blur"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:64","text":"指定投射纹理的 blur，范围为 0-1。该值会乘以 blurNear/blurFar 插值。当纹理不重复时，这会在投射颜色与填充颜色之间进行模糊。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:65","text":"S Blur Mult"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:66","text":"S 方向上的 Blur multiplier（模糊倍增）。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:67","text":"T Blur Mult"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:68","text":"T 方向上的 Blur multiplier（模糊倍增）。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:69","text":"Blur Near Dist"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:70","text":"从 cookie 起算，blur 插值开始的位置距离。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:71","text":"Blur Midpoint"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:72","text":"near 与 far 之间、midValue 所在位置的距离。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:73","text":"Blur Far Dist"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:74","text":"从 cookie 起算，blur 插值结束的位置距离。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:75","text":"Blur Near Value"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:76","text":"blur 插值开始处的 Blur multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:77","text":"Blur Mid Value"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:78","text":"blur 插值中间位置的 Blur multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:79","text":"Blur Far Value"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:80","text":"blur 插值结束处的 Blur multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:81","text":"Blur Exponent"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:82","text":"blur 插值的幂指数。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:83","text":"Density Falloff (for Analytic Mode Only)"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:84","text":"Density Near Dist"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:85","text":"从 cookie 起算，密度插值开始的位置距离。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:86","text":"Density Midpoint"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:87","text":"near 与 far 之间、midValue 所在位置的距离。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:88","text":"Density Far Dist"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:89","text":"从 cookie 起算，密度插值结束的位置距离。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:90","text":"Density Near Value"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:91","text":"模糊插值开始处的 Density multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:92","text":"Density Mid Value"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:93","text":"密度插值中间位置的 Density multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:94","text":"Density Far Value"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:95","text":"模糊插值结束处的 Density multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:96","text":"Density Exponent"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:97","text":"密度插值的幂指数。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:98","text":"Saturation, Contrast, Tint"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:99","text":"Saturation"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:100","text":"结果的 Saturation（0=灰度，1=正常，>1=增强颜色）。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:101","text":"Midpoint"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:102","text":"contrast 控制的 Midpoint。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:103","text":"Contrast"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:104","text":"Contrast control（小于 1 = 降低对比度，大于 1 = 提高对比度）。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:105","text":"White Point"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:106","text":"如果 (contrast > 1.0)，用于 contrast control 的 white point。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:107","text":"Tint"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:108","text":"经过 saturation、contrast 和 clamp 后所得颜色的 Tint。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:109","text":"Combine Mode"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:110","text":"Combine Mode"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:111","text":"mult"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:112","text":"：所有滤镜的结果会相乘。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:113","text":"max"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:114","text":"：使用所有滤镜中的最大结果。这最适合灰度灯光滤镜。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:115","text":"min"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:116","text":"：使用所有滤镜中的最小结果。这最适合灰度灯光滤镜。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:117","text":"screen"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:118","text":"：类似于 max 操作，但会以更平滑的方式组合渐变。这最适合灰度灯光。"}
{"item_id":"d4760927ed:119","text":"附加在灯光上的 Light filters 会按各自的 combine mode 分组。同一组中的 Light filters 会一起执行，并按 combine mode 进行组合。各组按以下顺序执行（max、min、screen，然后 mult），并且会相互相乘；这意味着 mult 组中把结果变黑的 filter 会将所有其他 filter 清零。"}
